### Phase 2: Database Schema (6 Tables)

#### [NEW] [source.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/models/source.py)
```
sources table:
  id (UUID PK)
  agent_type (enum: competitor|model_provider|research|hf_benchmark)
  name (str)
  url (str)
  feed_url (str, nullable)
  css_selectors (JSONB, nullable)
  keywords (JSONB, nullable)
  rate_limit_rpm (int, default 10)
  enabled (bool, default true)
  created_at, updated_at (timestamps)
```

#### [NEW] [snapshot.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/models/snapshot.py)
```
snapshots table:
  id (UUID PK)
  source_id (FK в†’ sources)
  run_id (FK в†’ runs)
  url (str)
  content_hash (str) вЂ” SHA256 of raw content
  raw_content (text)
  fetched_at (timestamp)
  http_status (int)
```

#### [NEW] [extraction.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/models/extraction.py)
```
extractions table:
  id (UUID PK)
  snapshot_id (FK в†’ snapshots)
  extracted_text (text)
  metadata (JSONB) вЂ” title, date, author, etc.
  extraction_method (str)
```

#### [NEW] [finding.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/models/finding.py)
```
findings table:
  id (UUID PK)
  run_id (FK в†’ runs)
  source_id (FK в†’ sources)
  title (str)
  date_detected (timestamp)
  source_url (str)
  publisher (str)
  category (enum: models|apis|pricing|benchmarks|safety|tooling)
  summary_short (text)
  summary_long (text)
  why_it_matters (text)
  evidence (JSONB)
  confidence (float, 0-1)
  tags (JSONB array)
  entities (JSONB) вЂ” company, model, dataset
  diff_hash (str)
  impact_score (float)
  is_duplicate (bool, default false)
  cluster_id (str, nullable)
  embedding (vector, nullable) вЂ” for similarity search
```

#### [NEW] [run.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/models/run.py)
```
runs table:
  id (UUID PK)
  started_at, completed_at (timestamps)
  status (enum: pending|running|completed|failed)
  agent_statuses (JSONB) вЂ” per-agent status
  total_findings (int)
  error_log (text, nullable)
```

#### [NEW] [digest.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/models/digest.py)
```
digests table:
  id (UUID PK)
  run_id (FK в†’ runs)
  date (date)
  executive_summary (text)
  pdf_path (str) вЂ” path to generated PDF
  email_sent (bool, default false)
  sent_at (timestamp, nullable)
  recipients (JSONB array)
```

---

### Phase 3: Core Pipeline Components

#### [NEW] [fetcher.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/core/fetcher.py)
- Async HTTP fetcher using `httpx` with retry + backoff
- Playwright fallback for JavaScript-rendered pages
- `robots.txt` checking via `robotexclusionrulesparser`
- Per-domain rate limiting (token bucket)
- Returns raw HTML/content + HTTP status

#### [NEW] [extractor.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/core/extractor.py)
- HTML to clean text via `trafilatura` (best-in-class article extraction)
- BeautifulSoup for CSS-selector-based targeted extraction
- RSS/Atom via `feedparser`
- Metadata extraction (title, date, author)

#### [NEW] [change_detector.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/core/change_detector.py)
- SHA256 content hashing for fast identical-page detection
- Text canonicalization (strip whitespace/boilerplate) before hashing
- Diff generation between previous and current snapshot
- Skip summarization if hash unchanged

#### [NEW] [summarizer.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/core/summarizer.py)
- LLM integration (Gemini primary, OpenAI fallback)
- Structured output extraction using JSON mode:
  - What changed, why it matters, who it affects, numbers/claims, citations
- Confidence scoring
- Guardrails: always include citations, never invent scores

#### [NEW] [dedup.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/core/dedup.py)
- Sentence-transformer embeddings for semantic similarity
- Cosine similarity threshold (>0.85 = likely duplicate)
- Cluster findings by topic using agglomerative clustering
- Categories: Models, APIs, Pricing, Benchmarks, Safety, Tooling

#### [NEW] [ranker.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/core/ranker.py)
Impact score formula from spec:
```
Impact = 0.35 * Relevance + 0.25 * Novelty + 0.20 * Credibility + 0.20 * Actionability
```
LLM-assisted scoring for each dimension (1-10 scale).

#### [NEW] [rate_limiter.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/core/rate_limiter.py)
- Token bucket per domain
- Configurable RPM per source
- Async-safe with `asyncio.Lock`

---

### Phase 4: Agent Workers

#### [NEW] [base_agent.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/agents/base_agent.py)
Shared interface all agents implement:
```python
class BaseAgent:
    async def run(run_id, agent_config, since_timestamp) -> list[Finding]
    # Uses: fetcher в†’ extractor в†’ change_detector в†’ summarizer
```

#### [NEW] [competitor_watcher.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/agents/competitor_watcher.py)
Agent #1: Discovers pages (RSS в†’ sitemap в†’ crawl), fetches, extracts, diffs, summarizes, ranks impact.

#### [NEW] [model_provider_watcher.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/agents/model_provider_watcher.py)
Agent #2: Tracks model releases, API updates, pricing changes. Extracts structured model metadata.

#### [NEW] [research_scout.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/agents/research_scout.py)
Agent #3: Queries arXiv, Semantic Scholar, OpenReview. Extracts core contribution, novelty, implications.

#### [NEW] [hf_benchmark_tracker.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/agents/hf_benchmark_tracker.py)
Agent #4: Scrapes HF leaderboards, trending models, SOTA claims. Tracks movements over time.

---

### Phase 5: Digest Compiler & Delivery

#### [NEW] [compiler.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/digest/compiler.py)
- Aggregates all findings from a run
- Calls dedup в†’ cluster в†’ rank
- Uses LLM to generate narrative sections per topic
- Produces executive summary (1-page constraint)

#### [NEW] [pdf_renderer.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/digest/pdf_renderer.py)
- Jinja2 HTML template в†’ WeasyPrint в†’ PDF
- Cover page with date + audience
- Executive summary section
- Deep-dive sections (Competitors, Model Providers, Research, HF Benchmarks)
- Appendix with source links

#### [NEW] [digest.html](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/digest/templates/digest.html)
Professional HTML template for PDF rendering with CSS print styles.

#### [NEW] [email_service.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/notifications/email_service.py)
- SendGrid SDK or SMTP fallback
- Sends: executive summary snippet, PDF attachment, dashboard link
- Configurable recipient list

---

### Phase 6: Orchestration & API

#### [NEW] [orchestrator.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/scheduler/orchestrator.py)
- Run Manager: creates run record, launches all 4 agents in parallel (`asyncio.gather`)
- Partial failure tolerant (one agent can fail, others continue)
- After agents complete: triggers digest compiler в†’ PDF в†’ email
- Per-URL retries with exponential backoff
- Domain-level circuit breaker

#### [NEW] [scheduler.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/scheduler/scheduler.py)
- APScheduler CronTrigger for daily runs
- Configurable run time and timezone
- Also exposes manual trigger via API

#### [NEW] [main.py](file:///c:/Bhuvan/zentivra/backend/app/main.py)
FastAPI app with:
- CORS middleware
- Startup: init DB, start scheduler
- Shutdown: cleanup

#### [NEW] REST API routes
- `POST /api/sources` вЂ” Add source
- `GET/PUT/DELETE /api/sources/{id}` вЂ” Manage sources
- `POST /api/runs/trigger` вЂ” Manual run trigger
- `GET /api/runs` вЂ” List runs history
- `GET /api/runs/{id}` вЂ” Run detail with agent statuses
- `GET /api/findings` вЂ” Browse findings (paginated, filterable)
- `GET /api/digests` вЂ” List digests
- `GET /api/digests/{id}/pdf` вЂ” Download PDF

---

### Phase 7: Web UI (Next.js)

#### [NEW] Next.js 14 App Router frontend

**Dashboard** (`/`):
- Today's digest summary card
- Latest run status
- Finding count by category (bar chart)
- Quick actions: trigger run, view latest PDF

**Sources Manager** (`/sources`):
- Table of all configured sources
- Add/edit/delete sources with form
- Toggle source enabled/disabled
- Filter by agent type

**Runs History** (`/runs`):
- Table of all runs with timestamps + status
- Click to view run detail with per-agent logs
- Visual badges for success/failure per agent

**Findings Explorer** (`/findings`):
- Searchable, filterable list of findings
- Filter by category, date range, agent, confidence
- Click to expand full finding detail
- Impact score visual indicator

**Digest Archive** (`/digests`):
- List of all generated digests by date
- Download PDF button
- Preview executive summary inline

